javadoc:
Manages changes and conflicts between the latest versioned Program and the
 Program that is being checked into version control.

methods.name: <init>
methods.comment: Construct a new manager for merging trees

params.name: resultProgram
params.comment:
latest version of the Program that is the 
 destination for changes applied from the source program

params.name: myProgram
params.comment:
source of changes to apply to the destination
 program

params.name: originalProgram
params.comment: program that was originally checked out

params.name: latestProgram
params.comment:
program that that is the latest version; the
 resultProgram and latestProgram start out as being identical

params.name: latestChangeSet
params.comment: change set of the destination program

params.name: myChangeSet
params.comment: change set for the source program

name: ProgramTreeMergeManager
comment:
